  "remarks": "YEi.012. Designation: Major General, Commander of the Houthi Air Force and Air Defense Forces. Ahmad al-Hamzi, the commander of the Houthi Air Force and Air Defense Forces, as well as its UAV program, plays a leading role in Houthi military efforts that directly threaten the peace, security, and stability of Yemen. Physical Description: Eye Color: Brown; Hair: Brown.; Listing: Listed by the 2140 Committee on 4 October 2022",
